(279, 221, '_form', '<p class="grid_12">1.申请人资料：</p>\n\n<p class="grid_2">你的名字<br />\n    [text your-name]\n</p> \n\n<p  class="grid_3">出生日期<br />\n[date your-dob]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_3">联系电话<br />\n[tel your-phone]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_3">你的邮箱<br />\n    [email your-email] </p>\n\n<p  class="grid_12">性别<br />\n[select your-sex "男" "女"]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_12">如在澳，所持签证类别<br />\n[text your-visa]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_3" >雅思成绩(或预测成绩):平均分 <br />\n[text your-ielts]\n<p class="grid_2" >听[text your-ielts-listen]</p>\n<p class="grid_2" >说[text your-ielts-speak]</p>\n<p class="grid_2" >读[text your-ielts-reading]</p>\n<p class="grid_2" >写[text your-ielts-writing]</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_12">雅思参加时间<br />\n[date your-ielts-date]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">2.学历情况:</p>\n\n\n<p class="grid_5">学历<br />\n[select your-degree "初中" "高中" "中专" "大专" "本科" "研究生" "博士生"]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_5">学制<br />\n[select your-study-year "2年" "3年" "4年" "5年"]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_3">最高学历毕业时间<br />\n[date your-graduate-date]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_4">毕业学校<br />\n[text your-graduate-school]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_4">专业<br />\n[text your-major]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">3.工作经验:</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">最近工作经验所从事职业<br />\n[textarea your-work-experience x10]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_5">最近工作经验起始时间\n[date your-start-date]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_5">最近工作经验结束时间\n[date your-finish-end]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">如有一段以上工作经验,请提供更多信息<br />\n[textarea your-more-experience x10]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">4.澳洲亲属情况:</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">如申请人在澳洲有亲属， 请填写：<br />\n[textarea your-relatives x10]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">是否澳洲永居或公民<br />\n[select your-relatives-visa "是" "否"]\n</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">5.澳洲学习情况:</p>\n\n<p class="grid_12">是否完成两年以上学习<br />\n[select study-in-au "是" "否"]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_4">专业<br />\n[text your-major-au]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_4">完成学习的时间<br />\n[date your-graduate-year-au]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_12">其他需要说明的情况或要求<br />\n[textarea your-other-status-au x10]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_12">您希望我们用哪种方式告知评估结果\n[select your-contact-way "电子邮件" "联系电话"]\n</p>\n\n<p  class="grid_3">[submit "发送"]</p>\n<p  class="grid_3"><input type="reset" value="重置" /></p>\n\n<br class="clear" />'),
