(396, 1, '2014-07-04 16:41:02', '2014-07-04 06:41:02', '<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>A.</span>免费移民评估</a></h3>\r\n专业顾问将为您进行免费移民评估，针对不同情况给出具体评估结果。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="../assessment">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>C.</span>定制移民计划</a></h3>\r\n专业顾问将为您量身定制整套移民方案，确保移民过程的安全可靠。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="../sevices/immigration">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>B.</span>申请各类学校</a></h3>\r\n不管你是哪类学生，专业留学顾问都会全力协助并精心设计你的学习方案。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="../servces/student">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="./contact"><span>D.</span>咨询服务</a></h3>\r\n位于悉尼市中心的办事处使您能很方便的找到我们，你可以给我们打电话或者发邮件获得实时的移民信息\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="../contact">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_12">\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_12">\r\n<div class="block2">\r\n<h3 class="upp">有问题吗?\r\n<br />\r\n咨询专家</h3>\r\n<div class="c_phone">(02) 9266 0318</div>\r\n<address>\r\n<br />\r\n周一到周五\r\n<br />\r\n早上9点到下午5点</address>\r\n<div class="grid_2 fright omega">\r\n<a href="../contact" class="chat">在线<br />咨询</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img1.jpg" />\r\n<h3>商业移民</h3>\r\n澳大利亚商业移民分为两类，一类是一步到位直接获永居的132类别，另一类是先申请4年临时居留签证，到澳洲建立生意2年或投资4年后再转永居。\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="../services/immigration">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img2.jpg" />\r\n<h3>家庭团聚</h3>\r\n澳大利亚家庭团聚分为配偶、子女、父母和最后一个亲属等几种。\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="../services/visa">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img3.jpg" />\r\n<h3>学生签证</h3>\r\n澳洲政府容许非澳洲市民或非永久居民在澳洲求学，任何非澳洲居民都有权提出留学申请，但同学必须获得学生签証才可以开始在澳洲留学。\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="../services/visa">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img4.jpg" />\r\n<h3>访问签证</h3>\r\n澳大利亚访问签证（600类别）允许申请人赴澳旅游、从事商务活动或探亲访友。该签证是一种临时签证。\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="../services/visa">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '396-2', '', '', '2014-07-04 16:53:04', '2014-07-04 06:53:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/southpac/?page_id=396', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(412, 1, '2014-07-04 17:30:28', '2014-07-04 07:30:28', 'Southpac Services is a professional migration consulting firm with headquarters in Sydney, Australia. Our firm has a single focus: to provide the best migration advice in the industry in order to get our clients the visa they want.\r\n\r\nWe’ll use our knowledge and experience to simplify the migration process, make sure your application package is perfect, and provide the best presentation of your case to the Department of Immigration and Border Protection (DIBP) or the MRT or RRT review tribunals. And if you’ve had a refusal or cancellation, we’ll sort it out and show you all your options – one of our specialties is solving immigration problems, no matter how difficult or complex. We’ll fight hard to get you the outcome you want.\r\n\r\nBut our work only begins when we lodge your visa application or appeal – after that we’re in close contact with the Department, and will handle all communications with the Department on your behalf, keeping you up to date 24/7 with all updates on your case.\r\n\r\nToday we live in a technology-driven world – our technology takes the entire visa application process online, and lets you communicate directly with the Registered Migration Agent assigned to your case. And we’ve simplified the visa application process so you only fill out one form – we’ll do the rest.\r\n\r\nWhat makes us different?\r\n\r\nKnowledge – Migration law and regulations are constantly changing, and our knowledge of current migration laws and regulations is first-rate. We publish Australia Visa News, a weekly newsletter that clients and others in the industry use to keep up to date on the latest migration law and regulation changes.\r\n\r\nExperience – We’re highly experienced with many visas including the latest legislation for employment, skilled, partner & family, student, visitor visas and others. As a Australian Registered Migration Agent, all of our work is conducted under a strict code of conduct.\r\n\r\nTransparency – We charge fixed fees so you can be confident of costs with no surprises. During your case you’ll know everything happening with your case 24/7 through our secure Client Portal.\r\nResults – We use our knowledge and experience to deliver what matters in the end: results. We’ll work hard to get you the visa you want.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '401-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-04 17:30:28', '2014-07-04 07:30:28', '', 401, 'http://localhost/southpac/401-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
